# Cursor Rules - Solux Hub

Source of truth: local Markdown files in this repo.

Always check before working:
- PROJECT_CONTEXT.md
- CURRENT_STATE.md
- DECISIONS.md
- TASKS.md

Also read (implementation truth):
- docs/ai/00_AI_INDEX.md and the files it links (ARCHITECTURE.md, FOLDER_STRUCTURE.md, etc.)

Keep .cursor/rules/project.mdc and CLAUDE.md consistent — update both when the doc sources change.

## Code Rules
- HTML project - keep it HTML-first
- Match existing style from Style_Guide.html
- Do not introduce JavaScript frameworks
- Keep inject-hypothesis.js scoped and minimal

## Change Rules
- Explain what files you changed and why
- Keep changes minimal and scoped
- Do not rewrite unrelated files
- Ask before changing document phase architecture (P01, P02, P03)
- Update docs when behavior changes
